data.description: Assumable VA loan w/ 2.25% interest rate (per seller), for those who qualify!! Call for more info. This country charmer is your next dream home with total privacy, beautiful views, tons of wildlife, 10 acres, a deer stand & your own pool! Roof & water heater only 4 years old. HVAC replaced just a few months ago. This 4 bedroom ranch features an open kitchen, dining & living area, 3 bedrooms & 2 full baths on the main level, plus an additional bedroom & half-bath in the basement! The basement includes a potential 5th bedroom (no egress), a 2nd living area, abundant storage & an unfinished space ready for your imagination! The outdoor space is the highlight of this home. The large front yard provides ample space for kids to play, plus the 2-car garage and plentiful parking! Out back, you'll find a chicken coop, storage shed, a spacious deck w/ storage below & a 27' pool w/ another large lawn area for the kids or dogs. Not to mention the 7+ acres of wooded acreage to explore, hunt & enjoy to the fullest! The woodstove in the living room can heat the home in the event of a power outage. Located just 5 miles from I-75 & 15 miles from Toyota. Selling As Is, but inspections welcome!
